{
  "id": "adv_main_02_13_04",
  "title": "東京編2章39話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。そっちはどうでした？\n何か異常は見つかりましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san‚ how did it go over there?\nDid you find anything unusual?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや、何もだ。天動さん達はどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ nothing. How about you‚ Tendo-san and the others?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 12.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ。スタッフさんに聞いても\n特に思い当たることはないそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. Even when I asked the staff‚\nno one seems to have noticed anything in particular.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 17.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、本当に姫野さんの手が回っているなら\n簡単に口を割るとも思えないですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the first place‚ if Himeno-san is really involved‚\nI don't think they would easily spill the beans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "闇雲に探し回ってても、埓が明かないか\nかといってこのまま、後手に回っても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Searching around blindly won't get us anywhere.\nBut if we just sit back and wait…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3033.3333333000032,
          "startTime": 32.2333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 32.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "あっれー？　そこに居るのは、まさかまさかの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my～? Could it be‚ those people there are‚ no way‚ no way…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 32.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 38.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "スリクス……\nそれに、姫野さん……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ⅢX…\nAnd Himeno-san…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 43.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-krk001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは\n大事な本番前に、こんな所で何をしているのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello.\nWhat are you doing here before such an important performance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "少々、捜し物をしていました\nですが……ちょうど良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were looking for something.\nBut… this is perfect timing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 54.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "単刀直入に聞きます\n今回は、何を仕掛けるつもりですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me ask you directly.\nWhat are you planning to do this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-krk002.m4a",
      "text": "仕掛ける？　ふふっ……\nまるで私が、罠でも仕掛けてるみたいに言うのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Planning? Hehe…\nYou make it sound like I'm setting some kind of trap.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 68.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "疑われて当然じゃないですか？\n今までだって、いろいろと仕掛けてきたんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's only natural to suspect you.\nYou've done all sorts of things in the past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ゴシップ記事をねつ造して、トリエルや私達を\n本番前に追い込んだり……あなたの得意分野ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You fabricated gossip articles and cornered TRINITYAiLE and us\nbefore the performance… It's your specialty‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 81.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-krk003.m4a",
      "text": "言いがかりはよしてちょうだい。あれらの記事は\n紛れもない事実だから報道されたんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please refrain from making false accusations. Those articles\nwere reported because they were undeniable facts‚ weren't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 91.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あれのどこが事実なんですか\nそうやってとぼけていられるのも今のうちですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What part of those was a fact?\nYou won't be able to play dumb for long.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-krk004.m4a",
      "text": "……そんな手垢まみれのセリフを吐く人、初めて見たわ\nふふっ、ホント、愚かな人なのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's the first time I've seen someone utter such a clichéd line.\nHehe‚ you really are a fool‚ aren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 107.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 107.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-krk005.m4a",
      "text": "大体、仮に何か仕掛けていたとしても\nバカ正直に言うはずがないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the first place‚ even if I were planning something‚\nthere's no way I would tell you so honestly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 113.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "それに関しては、姫野さんに同意です\n狡猾な人ですから、痕跡なんて残してないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree with Himeno-san on that.\nShe's a cunning person‚ she wouldn't leave any traces.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 122.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのみなさんは、そんなやり方で勝って\n嬉しいんですか？　満足出来るんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you happy to win with such methods‚ ⅢX?\nAre you satisfied?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 129.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さんが何を企んでいようと関係ないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn't matter what Himeno-san is planning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 133.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "私達は常に、全力を尽くして\n結果を勝ち取ってきたんだもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've always given it our all\nand earned our results.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 138.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-krk006.m4a",
      "text": "そう……この子達はあくまでも実力でのし上がってきた\n私はそれを支えているだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see… These girls have risen through the ranks with their skills.\nI'm just supporting them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "krk",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-krk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-krk007.m4a",
      "text": "やっていることの本質は貴方と同じよ\n星見プロのマネージャーさん……ふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The essence of what we're doing is the same as you‚\nHoshimi Pro's manager… Hehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3103933516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 153.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "違いますよ。{user}さんは\n何一つ、あなたと同じなんかじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. Manager-san\nis nothing like you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
